1.0     Version number bumped to 1.0

1.1	ADDED cgx overlay support (PicassoIV, CV64/3d, BV/CVPPC)
	FIXED CVID decoder bug on ARGB32 format screens during winplay
	when the anim size was not 16 pixel aligned (tricky bug)
	ADDED defaultpath tooltype, and requester appear when you select 
	a directory in the command line mode
	ADDED Apple Animation (RLE) 8 bit codec support (color/gray too)
	ADDED Apple Graphics (SMC) 8 bit codec support (color/gray too)
	(31.10.99)

1.2pre	Some pre-code for PPC version....
	(10.11.99)

1.2	FIXED a STORM dither bug (introducted in v1.2pre)
	FIXED RPZA modulo bug during non-aligned overlay playback
	FIXED PIP window dimensions
	FIXED MOV timer bug, which appeard when the mov timescale was more
	than the rate of the Amiga ECLOCK (reported by Pavel)
	Changes in PPC support code (now both WOS/PUP supported)
	ADDED PPC support for the following video dithers:
	32bit c2p, STORM dither (truecolor, hicolor) 
	ADDED PPC support for the following codecs Codecs:
	QuickTime SMC, QuickTime RLE, QT/AVI CinePak (ARGB32/BGR24/GRAY/Overlay)
	(06.02.2000)

1.3	FIXED CGX modeid requester cancel crash bug (strange, this not crashed under p96 cgx emu...)
	MODIFIED PIP window zoom y position (Hi Pavel! :)
	CORRECTED MOV header identification code
	FIXED MOV video timescale bug w. different frame time MOVs
	ADDED support for RGB 24 AVI files (Ultraconv AVI saver format)
	(06.08.2000)

1.4	ADDED JPEG/JFIF (MOV) codec support (8/24bit)
	FIXED RLE decoder p96 playback problem (strange, nobody reported this one before :)
	CHANGED PUBSCREEN stuff, now fall back to wb scren when specified pubscreen not found
	(26.12.2000)

1.5	ADDED CONTROL C (Break signal) checking stuff
	ADDED support for QT3/QT4/QT5 streaming MOV files (compressed header)
	ADDED 3IVX Delta 1/2 Codec support (3iv1)
	ADDED OpenDIVX (DIVX) Codec support - please note: it is disabled temporally
	ADDED QT 64bit filesupport	
	FIXED unsupported QT audio codecs frame size calculation (this caused I/O errors before)
	(20.05.2001)

1.6	Most biggest update ever.... :) So:
	FIXED CinePak decoder bufsize (PPC)
	FIXED CinePak decoder 2x1 block render (PPC/PIP)
	FIXED gui positioning problem over 65535 frames
	FIXED mace audio codec crash bug (QT)
	ADDED support for Divx3.11 (DIV3)
	ADDED support for OpenDivx/DIVX4/DIVX5.xx (DIVX/DX50)
	ADDED support for MPEG4/MPEG4 V1 (DIV1/MPG4/MP41)
	ADDED support for MPEG4 V2 (MP42)
	ADDED support for MPEG4 V3 (MP43)
	ADDED PPC optimised MJPEG/JPEG decoder (AVI/MOV)
	ADDED PPC optimised render for YUV422, YUV420P, YUV9 (overlay/hicolor)
	ADDED PPC optimised STORM render for all new codecs and for 3ivx (however faster/better quality will be added soon)
	FIXED varios problems in AVI header parser
	CHANGED AVI bufsize calculation
	ADDED new skipping methode (AVI/MOV)
	ADDED new skipping methode w/o audio playback (tolerant skip)
	ADDED delta render (PPC) for MPEG codecs (3IVX/DIVX clones) (can be controller via NODELTARENDER option/tooltype)
	ADDED NORENDER option/tooltype to disable rendering (usable for benchmarks)
	ADDED support for MPEGI/Layer2 audio (mp2)
	ADDED support for MPEGI/Layer3 audio (mp3)
	ADDED support for Sorenson Codecs (QT/SVQ1)
	ADDED support for QT6 filestructure
	ADDED support for MPEG4/QT6, however it is a bit buggy ATM... (will be fixed soon)
	FIXED some minor bugs in the MOV header parser
	(29.09.2002)
@endnode

